  <body>
    <section name="Introduction">
      <subsection name="What is the Feed Creator?">
        <p>
          <b>Feed Creator</b>
          was previously known as the RSS Feed Creator Project
        </p>
        <p>
          <b>Feed Creator</b>
          is an addon for Hippo CMS that lets you create
          <a href="http://cyber.law.harvard.edu/rss/rss.html">RSS feeds</a>,
          <a href="http://www.atomenabled.org/developers/syndication/atom-format-spec.php">ATOM feeds</a>
          and  provides an API which enables you to create your own web syndications
          with the CMS. You can create as many feeds as you like, and for each
          feed you can setup filters to determine which documents to include.
        </p>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Code base on GitHub">
        <p>The code of this project is on GitHub at <a href="https://github.com/bloomreach-forge/feeds/">https://github.com/bloomreach-forge/feeds/</a>.</p>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="Project compatibility">
        <p>
          See <a href="release-notes.html">Release notes</a> for compatibility.
        </p>
      </subsection>
      <subsection name="How can I use Feed Creator in my project?">
        <p>
          Follow the
          <a href="install.html">install</a>
          and
          <a href="usage.html">usage</a>
          instructions.
        </p>
      </subsection>
    </section>
